{"tid":866370,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(花生) 付出3年半 男友最後出軌","createTime":"2018-10-17T21:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T08:59:27.000Z","uid":119913,"like":9,"dislike":99,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"1795319e3877ee4d614b5dbe3b0523433736005b","tid":866370,"uid":119913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T21:26:21.000Z","msg":"同男朋友一齊左3年半 <br />\n佢呢幾年每份工都做唔長 <br />\n經濟緩助左好多 早兩個半月 我介紹左佢返尖沙咀一間bar既part time, <br />\n因為我同朋友都識個度d員工同老闆 <br />\n但佢自此成個人就變哂 <br />\n佢同我講 話翻正職份份都番唔長。<br />\n會係呢d場揾老細 食拖鞋飯 重叫我信佢 <br />\n呢兩個幾月 一星期 兩三日唔返屋企 <br />\n一係就朝早10點先返 又熄左機 又話自己部電話壞 最近重郁手打我 報左警 但心軟 無告佢 <br />\n最後今日無意中睇到佢電話 發現到d淫慾信息"},{"pid":"6adf70cbeb72a4f17ed4398317a6d8751558919b","tid":866370,"uid":119913,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T21:28:20.000Z","msg":"求屌醒"},{"pid":"09a2e40766eb060028e673172088e16691698959","tid":866370,"uid":119913,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T21:28:51.000Z","msg":"d信息仲係我電話度"},{"pid":"451207635f1754b9cedb5af4b65528b8ae35ec53","tid":866370,"uid":69026,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"quote":{"pid":"6adf70cbeb72a4f17ed4398317a6d8751558919b","tid":866370,"uid":119913,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T21:28:20.000Z","msg":"求屌醒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T21:29:24.000Z","msg":"仲未分手咁on9?"},{"pid":"683416efab5d620d765a44ba360abaac5d2f4c2b","tid":866370,"uid":26939,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T21:29:30.000Z","msg":"何必呢"},{"pid":"507c93921278aadf7e01ecb992e8f96c98be5aa2","tid":866370,"uid":51684,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T21:30:05.000Z","msg":"其實你開得post都有答案"},{"pid":"61dbaac4895d5be9ac30c6f01529f585a09ef90a","tid":866370,"uid":131980,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T21:30:27.000Z","msg":"點解你咁可以為左佢去到咁賤<br />\n付出多=難放手"},{"pid":"f4163bb44077de026355932365dbc69dc4327e6b","tid":866370,"uid":189264,"like":18